#SQL

This folder contains the SQL component of the project, including the scripts used to explore and analyze the dataset, as well as the corresponding query outputs.

## Contents

scripts– SQL scripts for data exploration, aggregation, and analytical queries.
outputs– Results generated from executing the SQL scripts, demonstrating key findings and query outputs.

The SQL analysis focuses on summarizing global NCD mortality rates, identifying trends, and comparing mortality across countries, regions, and time.
